author: JUN K
title: On the 21st, Seoul SK will hold a "usky party" to commemorate its regular league victory against Uls.. - MK
text:
On the 21st, Seoul SK will hold a "usky party" to commemorate its regular league victory against Ulsan Hyundai Mobis at Jamsil Student Gymnasium.
After the game, SK will hold a regular league victory ceremony with its fans and the players will present goods to the fans to commemorate the victory at the site.
Before the game, a photo zone displaying the regular league championship trophy in the outer square will be operated to provide fans with an opportunity to take pictures against the backdrop of the championship trophy. The trophy photo zone will also be operated in the game on the 23rd.
The first 1,000 spectators who enter the game will be given free Baekseolgi rice cakes to commemorate the regular league victory.
In addition, SK will sell winning goods such as shirt-type replica, upcycling crossbag, winning logo T-shirts, and winning logo hats to fans at the goods shop in the stadium.
Meanwhile, SK will play in a uniform with the regular league championship logo from the game.
[MIN JUN KU, MK Sports Reporter]
